; Coverage test for history.cc L488 and multi-hop price conversion
; Tests triangular price conversion GBP -> EUR -> $ which exercises the
; dijkstra shortest path traversal and the last_target = v_comm branch.

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/01/01 GBP 1.17 EUR

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    10 GBP
    Assets:Cash     -10 GBP

test bal -X '$'
             $-12.87  Assets:Cash
              $12.87  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
